## **Vehicle Showroom Management System - Complete Application Specification**

### **Project Overview**
Build a full-stack vehicle showroom management application for 2-wheelers (extensible to 4-wheelers) using React and Tailwind CSS. The application should handle the complete customer journey from inquiry to delivery, including inventory management, booking, documentation, and sales processing with Indian taxation compliance.

---

### **Core Modules & Features**

#### **1. User Management & Authentication**
- **Customer Portal**: Registration, login, profile management
- **Admin/Staff Portal**: Role-based access (Sales Executive, Manager, Accountant, Documentation Officer)
- **User Roles & Permissions**: Define what each role can view/edit
- **Profile Features**: Save preferences, view booking history, track order status

#### **2. Vehicle Catalog & Inventory Management**
- **Vehicle Categories**: Scooters, Motorcycles, Electric 2-wheelers (prepare for 4-wheeler expansion)
- **Brand & Model Management**: Multiple brands with their model lineup
- **Variant System**: Each model can have multiple variants (Standard, Deluxe, Sports, etc.)
- **Color Options**: Maintain color availability per variant
- **Specifications Display**: 
  - Engine details (CC, power, torque)
  - Mileage, fuel type
  - Features list
  - Dimensions and weight
  - Braking system, suspension
  - Warranty details
- **Pricing Structure**:
  - Ex-showroom price
  - RTO charges (state-specific)
  - Insurance (Third-party mandatory, comprehensive optional)
  - Accessories cost
  - Extended warranty options
  - AMC packages
- **Stock Management**: Real-time inventory tracking, color-wise availability, incoming stock alerts

#### **3. Inquiry Management System**
- **Inquiry Form**: Capture customer details, interested vehicle, preferred color, budget range
- **Lead Tracking**: Assign inquiries to sales executives
- **Follow-up System**: Schedule calls, meetings, test rides
- **Status Pipeline**: New → Contacted → Test Ride Scheduled → Negotiation → Hot Lead → Converted/Lost
- **Notes & Communication Log**: Record all interactions with customer
- **Lead Scoring**: Priority marking based on purchase probability

#### **4. Vehicle Comparison Tool**
- Compare up to 3-4 vehicles side-by-side
- Compare specifications, features, pricing
- Highlight differences in color-coded format

#### **5. Booking & Reservation System**
- **Booking Process**:
  - Select vehicle, variant, and color
  - Choose accessories and add-ons
  - Calculate total price with all charges
  - Pay booking amount (configurable: ₹5,000 - ₹20,000)
  - Generate booking confirmation
- **Booking Management**:
  - View all bookings (customer & admin)
  - Cancel/modify bookings (within policy)
  - Refund processing
  - Waiting list for out-of-stock colors

#### **6. Accessories & Add-ons Module**
- **Accessory Categories**:
  - Safety (helmets, riding jackets, knee guards)
  - Convenience (mobile holders, USB chargers, luggage carriers)
  - Protection (body covers, crash guards, tank pads)
  - Performance (performance exhaust, air filters)
  - Aesthetics (stickers, custom seats, LED lights)
- **Vehicle-Specific Compatibility**: Link accessories to compatible models
- **Bundle Offers**: Create accessory packages with discounts
- **Pricing**: Individual pricing with GST breakdown

#### **7. Indian Taxation & Charges Calculator**
Implement accurate calculation as per Indian regulations:

**A. RTO Charges (State-specific)**:
- Registration fees
- Road tax (based on vehicle cost and state)
- Smart card/number plate charges
- Hypothecation charges (if financed)
- Special/fancy number fees (optional)

**B. Insurance**:
- Third-party insurance (mandatory, IRDAI rates)
- Comprehensive insurance (optional, based on IDV)
- Zero depreciation add-on
- Personal accident cover (mandatory for owner)

**C. GST Structure**:
- 28% GST on vehicles (2-wheelers up to 350cc)
- 18% GST on accessories
- Cess charges (if applicable)

**D. Other Charges**:
- Extended warranty
- AMC (Annual Maintenance Contract)
- FastTag
- Accessories fitting charges
- Documentation charges

**Price Breakdown Display**:
```
Ex-showroom Price: ₹XX,XXX
RTO & Registration: ₹X,XXX
Insurance: ₹X,XXX
Accessories: ₹X,XXX
Other Charges: ₹XXX
------------------------
On-Road Price: ₹XX,XXX
```

#### **8. Finance & Loan Integration**
- **Loan Calculator**: EMI calculator with interest rates
- **Bank/NBFC Partners**: Multiple financing options
- **Loan Application**: Collect documents, submit to financier
- **Approval Tracking**: Track loan status
- **Down Payment Options**: Flexible down payment schemes

#### **9. Documentation Management**
- **Customer Documents Required**:
  - Identity proof (Aadhar, PAN, Voter ID)
  - Address proof
  - Income proof (for loans)
  - Passport-size photographs
- **Document Upload**: Secure upload and storage
- **Verification Status**: Track document verification
- **RTO Documentation**: Generate Form 20, 21, 22 as required
- **Invoice Generation**: Tax invoice with HSN codes
- **Digital Signature**: E-sign capability for agreements

#### **10. Sales Process Workflow**
Complete pipeline from inquiry to delivery:

**Stage 1: Inquiry** → Capture lead details
**Stage 2: Follow-up** → Assign sales executive, schedule interactions
**Stage 3: Test Ride** → Book and conduct test rides
**Stage 4: Quotation** → Generate detailed quotation with all charges
**Stage 5: Booking** → Collect booking amount, confirm order
**Stage 6: Documentation** → Collect and verify documents
**Stage 7: Finance Processing** (if applicable) → Loan approval
**Stage 8: Payment** → Collect full payment or finance approval
**Stage 9: Invoice & Registration** → Generate invoice, initiate RTO registration
**Stage 10: Pre-Delivery Inspection** → PDI checklist completion
**Stage 11: Delivery** → Hand over vehicle with documents
**Stage 12: Post-Sales** → Follow-up, service reminders

#### **11. Payment Gateway Integration**
- **Payment Modes**: UPI, Credit/Debit Card, Net Banking, Wallets
- **Payment Types**: 
  - Booking amount
  - Full payment
  - Installment payments
  - Down payment for finance
- **Payment Receipts**: Auto-generate receipts
- **Refund Management**: Process cancellations and refunds
- **Payment Tracking**: Link payments to bookings/sales

#### **12. Test Ride Management**
- **Booking System**: Schedule test rides with date/time slots
- **Availability Calendar**: Sales executive and vehicle availability
- **Customer Verification**: Check license validity
- **Waiver/Agreement**: Digital consent form
- **Feedback Collection**: Post test ride feedback

#### **13. Reports & Analytics Dashboard**
- **Sales Reports**: Daily/monthly/yearly sales, revenue
- **Inventory Reports**: Stock levels, aging inventory
- **Lead Conversion**: Conversion ratio, funnel analysis
- **Financial Reports**: Payment collection, pending amounts
- **Performance Metrics**: Sales executive performance
- **Customer Insights**: Popular models, colors, accessories
- **Tax Reports**: GST returns data, TDS reports

#### **14. Notification System**
- **Email Notifications**: Booking confirmation, payment reminders, delivery updates
- **SMS Alerts**: OTP, important updates
- **In-app Notifications**: Status updates, offers
- **WhatsApp Integration**: Order updates, documents sharing

#### **15. Customer Portal Features**
- **Dashboard**: View booking status, payment history
- **Document Upload**: Submit required documents
- **Track Order**: Real-time status tracking
- **Service Booking**: Schedule service appointments
- **Payment History**: Download receipts and invoices
- **Support Tickets**: Raise queries/complaints

#### **16. Admin Dashboard**
- **Overview**: Sales summary, pending tasks, alerts
- **Inquiry Management**: View and assign leads
- **Booking Management**: All bookings, status updates
- **Inventory Control**: Add/update vehicles, manage stock
- **User Management**: Add staff, manage roles
- **Price Management**: Update prices, taxes, offers
- **Reports Center**: Generate various reports
- **Settings**: Configure taxes by state, policies, terms

